      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WYNDRA ALL SASS (1) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (24.04) at this track. Looks the one to beat on her best form. ZIPPING KORDA (2) goes very well this course and distance starting eight times for four wins and three minors. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (23.78) in a Grade 3/4 over 407m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. FAST FREDDY (3) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 23.91 beating Legends Told. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to his name from seven starts. Sure to be thereabouts. BRIGHT SIDE (6) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
